772
01:34:37,987 --> 01:34:41,237
There's a sign to Sir Drake Boulevard!

773
01:34:41,908 --> 01:34:43,782
Not this one.

774
01:34:44,410 --> 01:34:45,786
I want my mother.

775
01:34:47,080 --> 01:34:48,111
Shut up!

776
01:34:50,166 --> 01:34:51,743
Just get to the right!

777
01:35:06,684 --> 01:35:08,261
